seller.oneLinerTitle: Virtual Assistant for Data Entry, B2B Lead Generation and SkipTracing
seller.description:
It's me, Habiba, a Virtual Assistant with extensive experience in the real estate industry. 

I lead a team of 20 people, and we are here to help you with any types of Data Entry, Data Mining, Copy Paste and other administrative support services. 

We can also help you with real estate property research and skip tracing for any property within the USA. Let's talk business!

certifications.certificationName: Work From Home As A Virtual Assistant

reviews.comment: Habiba was very responsive but there was quite a lot of detail missing in the items Habiba was able to accomplish, without stating a reason as to why there was so much missing. It was only 2 hours of work to start but the info entered was out of order. Maybe they had a strategy but it wasn't worth trying to go back and forth. Easier to find another seller for a longer time period.

I am not techie. When I first received the work, I couldn't figure out how to open it. So she sent it a different way. She under promised and over delivered. I would use her again! She is a 'real find'.

Highly recommend! I needed help with some research on a very niche topic for my daughters birthday party. I asked for data entry into a template I created. Everything was delivered as expected within a few hours and I was impressed with communication and ability to follow directions and apply feedback.

After a quite long time the task was completed successfully, the communication was good but the scope of the task was not understood at first. After 2 requests of changing the delivery date since it took more time than expected, the order was delivered. The quality was ok

Exactly what I asked for in less time than expected. A sample was sent in advance 
for approval to ensure the project was done correctly. The price point was more than reasonable. I already have another project to send over.
Happy to work with her again :)
I loved working with her. She is best and humble person. Thank you :)

Outstanding Experience !!! Habiba has great communication skills, friendly and cooperative nature. She make sure to provide me everything related project on time. Like to work with her again. Thank you :)
